<h4 class="margin-top">What are Interesting Technology Advances You're Personally Excited About?</h4>

<p>
	“I’m very excited about IoT because the opportunities are wide open. It feels like the very early days of the internet again. You have smart thermostats, smart lights, and smart everything. The problem I find interesting is how to control everything. Currently, you need to open individual apps to use each device, but there needs to be a better solution. It’s like watching android and apple all over again. There is opportunity to bring real change to people’s lives.”
</p>

<p>
	“In developing nations, mobile is huge. You are seeing people come on to mobile and skip the PC industry entirely. Traditional card payments do not work in developing countries - there are mobile payments instead. In Southeast Asia, they skipped the credit card industry completely and went directly to mobile.”
</p>

